main.model

Class Playlist

  • java.lang.Object
    • main.model.Playlist

  • public class Playlist
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is for the playlist. The playlists contain the songs that the user has added to the application. The Song Library is a special kind of playlist, as it contains every song that the user has added and the song library cannot be removed.

        The constructior for the playlist.
        Parameters:
        playlistID - The unique id for the playlist. SongLibrary has the id=1
        playlistName - The name for the playlist
        playlistDescription - The description of the playlist, optional
        isLibrary - If the playlist is the SongLibrary, this value is True. Otherwise it will be false.
